---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Support the Club - Great Catholic Book Club"
  description="Great Catholic Book Club exists to build something beautiful for God and tell people about Jesus. If the work has been worth something to you, consider becoming a patron."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-black-olive relative">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat" style="background-image: url('/images/SiteImages/A vast dimly lit library full of ancient interesting and colorful books.jpg');"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black-olive/80 via-black-olive/90 to-black-olive/95"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-champaign-100 mb-6 font-headline drop-shadow-lg">
          Support the Club
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-champaign-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Every great library needs patrons. Be one of ours.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Personal Story Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-black-olive">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="bg-black-olive border border-champaign-700/30 rounded-lg p-8 shadow-2xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <img
            src="/images/SiteImages/TylerAndSadie.png"
            alt="Tyler and Sadie Woodley"
            class="w-48 h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-champaign-700/30 mx-auto"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="text-champaign-200 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
          <p class="text-lg text-champaign-100 font-medium">
            GCBC is Tyler and Sadie's passion project, built by a family of six in Iowa who love great books and love Jesus.
          </p>
          <p>
            The study guides, the videos, the blog, the monthly discussions are all free, and we're working hard to keep them that way. And also, keeping the club running takes real time and real money: books, hosting, research, writing, design, and more.
          </p>
          <p>
            If GCBC has brought you something good (a great book recommendation, a fresh angle on a story you loved, or just the knowledge that someone else out there studies every book through the Catholic lens), consider buying us a coffee. It goes directly toward keeping the pages turning.
          </p>
          <p>
            No membership, no commitment. Just two people doing something they love, grateful for the company.
          </p>
          <p class="text-champaign-100 font-semibold font-headline text-center pt-2">
            &mdash; Tyler &amp; Sadie
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Support Tiers Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-black-olive border-t border-champaign-700/20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-champaign-100 mb-4 font-headline text-center">
        Choose Your Support
      </h2>
      <p class="text-champaign-300 text-center mb-12">
        One-time contribution. No recurring charges, no obligations.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <!-- The Bookmark — $5 -->
        <article class="bg-black-olive border border-champaign-700/30 rounded-lg p-8 shadow-xl flex flex-col">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-champaign-100 font-headline mb-2">$5</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-rust-400 font-headline mb-3">The Bookmark</h3>
            <p class="text-champaign-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              You're keeping the lights on. We'll put it toward the next month's book.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-auto">
            <a
              href="https://square.link/u/2p4rptG7"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="block w-full border border-champaign-700 text-champaign-100 text-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-champaign-700/20 transition-colors"
            >
              Give $5
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- The Paperback — $10 -->
        <article class="bg-black-olive border border-rust-800/60 rounded-lg p-8 shadow-xl flex flex-col relative">
          <!-- Most popular indicator -->
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
            <span class="bg-rust-800 text-champaign-100 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
              Most Common
            </span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-champaign-100 font-headline mb-2">$10</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-rust-400 font-headline mb-3">The Paperback</h3>
            <p class="text-champaign-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              You're buying us a book. Literally. This covers a month's reading selection.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-auto">
            <a
              href="https://square.link/u/dhFzjdqG"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="block w-full bg-rust-800 text-champaign-100 text-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-rust-900 transition-colors shadow-md"
            >
              Give $10
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- The Patron — $25 -->
        <article class="bg-black-olive border border-champaign-700/30 rounded-lg p-8 shadow-xl flex flex-col">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-champaign-100 font-headline mb-2">$25</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-rust-400 font-headline mb-3">The Patron</h3>
            <p class="text-champaign-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              You're naming a wing of the library. We're genuinely grateful.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-auto">
            <a
              href="https://square.link/u/fNOWxE0y"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="block w-full border border-champaign-700 text-champaign-100 text-center px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-champaign-700/20 transition-colors"
            >
              Give $25
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>

      <!-- Fine print -->
      <p class="text-center text-champaign-300 text-sm mt-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Payments processed securely by Square. This is a one-time payment, not a tax-deductible charitable donation. No recurring charges.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-rust-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-champaign-100 mb-4 font-headline">
        Come Read With Us
      </h2>
      <p class="text-champaign-200 mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Supporting the club is never required. Come join the conversation.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <a href="/books" class="inline-block bg-champaign-100 text-rust-800 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-champaign-200 transition-colors shadow-md">
          View Reading List
        </a>
        <a href="/join" class="inline-block bg-rust-600 text-champaign-100 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-rust-700 transition-colors shadow-md">
          Join the Club
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
